      {
        "q": "What language is used?",
        "a": "Ingeri International School follows the French national curriculum. French is the main language, with an opening to English and Kinyarwanda."
      },
      {
        "q": "Is there catering on site?",
        "a": "Yes, balanced, varied and locally sourced meals are prepared every day. Children take part in table routines."
      },
      {
        "q": "How does the settling-in period work?",
        "a": "Progressive settling-in: prior visits with parents, short stays that gradually lengthen, respecting the child's own pace."
      },
